                    Corporate RBT
                </div>
                <p>After the amazing success of Warid’sCallerTunes, we bring to you an amazing new solution custom made for your organization’s advertising needs! Make your presence felt with Warid’s Corporate RBT!</p>
                <p>With Corporate RBT, customers/organizations can activate their company’s custom made ringtones on their company’s mobile numbers and communicate their new products, offers or news about their company to their valued customers.</p>
                <p>Anyone calling your company’s numbers will now hear your company’s custom made ringtone which can serve as advertisement for your firm and its products!</p>
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        The corporate  customer signs up for Corporate RBT service for a nominal one time activation  fee and monthly charges of Rs. 30 per month for every number on which Corporate  RBT is to be activated.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Warid&rsquo;s Corporate RBT  system then plays the customized ringtone to any caller who calls the number on  which customized RBT has been set by the company.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Corporate RBT will  not interfere with personal/default RBT after its assigned time slot. However,  Corporate RBT will always take precedence over personal RBT in case its  assigned time slot overlaps with personal RBT.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Only Warid  subscribers can be activated with this service.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        In case Corporate RBT  is activated on a number which already has Caller Tunes activated, then monthly  charges for that number will be Rs 30+tax/month for Corporate RBT in addition  to normal CallerTune monthly charges of Rs. 30+tax.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>How to acquire Warid’s Corporate RBT Solution</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        If you are a Warid  customer, please contact your designated Corporate Sales/CAM and he/she will  assist you in acquiring this solution.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        If your organization  does not have a Warid CAM assigned to it, please email <a href="mailto:corporaterbt@waridtel.com">corporaterbt@waridtel.com</a>&nbsp;for information and assistance on how to acquire this  solution.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        The length of the  customized ringtone should not be longer than 30 seconds.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        The ringtone will be  applied to the company&rsquo;s uploaded list of numbers provided that this list of  numbers is in the ownership of the company.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
                <p>
                    Warid reserves the right to reject and delete the Ringtone/Corporate RBT if:
                    “The Ringtone/Corporate RBT contains elements which render the Content or any part thereof unlawful, threatening, malicious, obscene, pornographic, profane, misleading, defamatory or otherwise prohibited for distribution inter alia, in the Territory”.
                </p>
